reviewText: What a cute show! Never caught it when it was on the air, but I picked it up as a dollar movie at Walmart for my little girl (she's 5) and she absolutely LOVES it. It's all she wants to play on the DVD player in the car.
This dvd is junk.  I thought I would be able to use it for my k-2 classes to teach from,  not the case.  Don't waste your money.  I do not recommend buying this dvd.
